spieler
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a gambler, a swindler, a card sharp, a con man
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:spieling
Pronunciation:
Notes: spieling		sometimes spelt speeler, for which note homonym re speedy horse
